[[Classes]]: {{Class|Inventory}}&rarr;{{Class|ScoreItem}}&rarr;<u>EvilSceptre</u><br>

The third kind of bonus item in the press-release beta version of Doom. The first two (a "demonic dagger" and a "skull chest") were turned into useful items ({{Class|HealthBonus|health bonus}} and {{Class|ArmorBonus|armor bonus}} respectively) but this one and the {{Class|UnholyBible|unholy bible}} were simply discarded.

It has no purpose except counting towards the number of items that are tallied on the "level finished" screen.

